import React from 'react';
import { Box, Button, Text, Card, CardHeader,CardFooter,CardBody} from 'grommet';
import { Server, Magic } from 'grommet-icons';


function CardsForm() {
    return(
        <Box direction="row" gap="large" pad="medium">
          <Card  height="small" width="medium" background="purple">
                <CardHeader>
                  <Button icon={<Magic />} onClick={() => {}} />
                </CardHeader>
                <CardBody pad={{horizontal: "small"}}>
                <Text weight="bold">Customs Annexure </Text>
                <Text size="xsmall">Part A, B, C, D, E, F, G</Text>
                </CardBody>
                <CardFooter pad="small"> 
                  <Button primary label="Start Tour" size="small" color="#00567A"/>
                </CardFooter>
          </Card>

          <Card  height="small" width="medium" background="brand">
                <CardHeader>
                  <Button icon={<Server />} onClick={() => {}} />
                </CardHeader>
                <CardBody pad={{horizontal: "small"}}>
                <Text weight="bold">Asset Tracker</Text>
                <Text size="xsmall">Part E, F, G</Text>
                </CardBody>
                <CardFooter pad={{horizontal: "small"}}>
                  <Button primary label="Launch" size="small" color="#00567A"/>
                </CardFooter>
          </Card>

        </Box>  
    );
}


export default CardsForm;
